mages-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/abbi-jacobson-Kevin-WinterGetty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/abbi-jacobson-Kevin-WinterGetty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/abbi-jacobson-Kevin-WinterGetty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/abbi-jacobson-Kevin-WinterGetty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《A League Of Their Own》</em>的创作者猛烈抨击<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊 Prime Video</a> ，称其取消该节目的理由是“胡扯”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/strike-actors-writers-hollywood-when-will-it-end-3477098">好莱坞罢工！关于演员和作家抗议的每个问题都得到了解答</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部喜剧改编自 1992 年麦当娜主演的同名电影，讲述了二战期间组建棒球联盟的妇女们的故事。</p><p>该剧的第二季已在 Prime Video 上订购，但本周宣布不会继续播出，该流媒体服务将取消与好莱坞正在进行的罢工联系在一起。</p><p>现在，创作者兼明星艾比·雅各布森 (Abbi Jacobson) 在 Instagram 上猛烈抨击 Prime 对这一决定的解释。</p><p>她写道：“我很幸运能够讲述这些故事并扮演这个我非常喜欢的角色。人生多么难得啊。所以我今天很伤心。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwG36Vapnlx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><p></p><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; borde